{"tid":977324,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"訓左冇睇隻為錢去大陸做狗既人形豬屌左保皇狗未？","createTime":"2019-01-11T05:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T13:19:19.000Z","uid":38523,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e677d0aaeb8caae08cdd26d1776d64ad7afca258","tid":977324,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:59:27.000Z","msg":"人形豬關愛座hunter呢？<br />\n平時大大聲過泛民保皇狗一樣<br />\n依加大好機會比位佢入保皇狗等老野知道保皇狗令佢地要65歲先可以申請綜援<br />\n佢竟然都係扮盲<br />\n睇下佢profile<br />\n關愛座hunter你隻大陸間碟仲有咩借口？"},{"pid":"c2a2c1ee7bb9ba1153eed4cc2316a033254d57a3","tid":977324,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:05:43.000Z","msg":"今次你隻大陸間碟冇借口啦掛<br />\n平時打住泛民同保皇狗一樣既口號<br />\n但就只係屌泛民<br />\n今次咁大個位<br />\n你加入扮盲扮到幾時？<br />\n大家可以入去呢隻大陸間碟profile睇下<br />\n我一早都話<br />\n一個雨革後為錢去大陸做狗既人形豬<br />\n信得過就奇啦"},{"pid":"e93782c7122e20ad663e58602c17712e6f034c3b","tid":977324,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:15:15.000Z","msg":"。。。。。"},{"pid":"c156aa42c7fa00b7f86aef45748a1ca58e088242","tid":977324,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"1254d83621c6c118687d395610a07a75f0e0b058","tid":977324,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:29:07.000Z","msg":"係外國生活如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天氣凍記住著多件褸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔使理楊onq架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca619bd92446ee02eb90f80eb535a3adfe6cc0c","tid":977324,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:35:44.000Z","msg":"再互屌都冇用"},{"pid":"d819a39b2992cfecf30c377acbba4b6f9c053ba2","tid":977324,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:46:06.000Z","msg":"。。。。。。"},{"pid":"2d58d87dcf1574ee0940a26bc254353c3c16269c","tid":977324,"uid":385